Output docs/demo/ace-lint-getting-started.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "cd ace-lint"
Enter

Type "ace-lint README.md"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "ace-lint lib/ace/lint/version.rb --type ruby --fix"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "ace-lint --doctor"
Enter
Sleep 2s
